    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那这个报文需要完整展示TCP头部字段吗？比如Source Port和Destination Port这些标准字段，还有像ACK、SYN这样的标志位？",
      "elements_involved": [
