    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标准头部都要有。特别注意的是106到111位那几个标志位——URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN，工业控制里ACK和URG的优先级判断很关键。另外Window字段也要标出来，用于流量控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Window"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础结构：0-15位Source Port，16-31位Destination Port，32-63位Sequence Number，64-95位Acknowledgment Number，然后是Data Offset和Reserved。标志位区域按您说的放在106-111位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "在标准头部之后，我需要加一个自定义字段。160-191位留给IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，这是我们的设备控制逻辑层。最后192-223位放实际data载荷。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "data"
